CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

January 9, 2004

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1985-0007. State v. Williams.

Cuyahoga App. No. 47853. Upon consideration of appellant’s second pro se motion to vacate this court’s order setting January 14, 2004 execution date,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be and hereby is denied.
